    PERSONAL_li6: "Other information, obtained during our KYC procedures, such as information about your financial state and source of funds;",
    PERSONAL_li7_APP: "We also automatically collect certain computer, device, and browsing information when you access the Site, the App, or use the Services. We record your usage of the App with Smartlook. This information is aggregated to provide statistical data about our users' browsing actions and patterns, and does not personally identify individuals.",
