    RETENTION: "RETENTION OF PERSONAL INFORMATION",
    RETENTION_P1: "We retain Personal Information for as long as necessary to fulfill purposes described in this Privacy Policy, subject to our own legal and regulatory obligations. By our record-keeping obligations, we will retain account and other Personal Information for at least five years after termination of the respective agreement.",
